headline.print_headline: Marquez Takes Record 13th Pole in Malaysia
headline.main: Marquez Takes Record 13th Pole in Malaysia

lead_paragraph: Reigning world champion Marc Marquez of Spain clinched a record 13th pole in the MotoGP season at the Malaysian Grand Prix at Sepang on Saturday.
